SonarQube - for continuous inspection of code quality to perform automatic reviews with static analysis of code to detect bugs, code smells and vulnerabilities
 
 SonarQube vs SonarQube Scanner:-
 ---------------------------------
 SonarQube :- central server holding the result of analysis
 
 SonarQube Scanner :- performs analysis and sends the results to SonarQube server



Working with SonarQube :-

Download the SonarQube Community Edition.
Unzip it, let's say in D:\sonarqube
Start the sonar server > StartSonar
Login to http://localhost:9000 with System Admin credentials - admin/admin
